Here if first person wants second person to get the pencil and throw it away

54
00:03:05.070 --> 00:03:09.230
 person1 should provide a clear instruction to person2

55
00:03:09.230 --> 00:03:10.740
This is known as a task.

56
00:03:10.800 --> 00:03:16.090
and using this first  person gets a job done using second person 


57
00:03:16.150 --> 00:03:20.930
Similarly if a person wants to get a job done by a computer

58
00:03:20.930 --> 00:03:25.450
 he should provide a clear instruction in the computer known language. 

59
00:03:25.460 --> 00:03:28.970
For example to add two numbers A and B 

60
00:03:28.970 --> 00:03:31.429
He should give instructions like this 

61
