int a=10; int b= 20; int sum = a+b;

62
00:03:37.340 --> 00:03:40.550
Here this step by step instructions is known as the program 

63
00:03:40.555 --> 00:03:43.790
so a collection of instructions that performs a specific task 

64
00:03:43.790 --> 00:03:48.190
is known as a computer program.

65
00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:49.990
And to accomplish various tasks using computer 

66
00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:52.760
we need to write various programs 

67
